---
import PageLayout from "@layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout
  title="Mentric for Independent Coaches — Elevate Your Coaching Practice"
  description="Mentric gives independent coaches the tools to run a professional, structured practice — without the admin burden. Assessments, session management, CPD tracking, and more."
>
  <!-- ─── Hero ─── -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-glow-gradient">
    <div class="section-container py-10 md:py-14 text-center">
      <p class="category-label mb-4">For Independent Coaches</p>
      <h1 class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        Your practice, <span class="text-primary">elevated</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg md:text-xl">
        Everything you need to run a professional, structured coaching practice
        — without drowning in admin. Focus on what you do best: coaching.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary-lg">Book a Demo</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Pain Points ─── -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="section-container py-14">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10">
        <p class="category-label mb-4">The reality</p>
        <h2>Sound familiar?</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="card-editorial p-8">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary-light flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 6A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 6 3.75h2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 10.5 6v2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25H6a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25V6ZM3.75 15.75A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 6 13.5h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25 2.25V18a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25H6A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 3.75 18v-2.25ZM13.5 6a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25-2.25H18A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 20.25 6v2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 18 10.5h-2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25V6ZM13.5 15.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25-2.25H18a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25 2.25V18A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 18 20.25h-2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25v-2.25Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-2">Scattered tools</h4>
          <p class="text-base">
            Juggling spreadsheets, calendars, and notes across multiple apps
            — and still feeling like things slip through the cracks.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-editorial p-8">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary-light flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 3 19.875v-6.75ZM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V8.625ZM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V4.125Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-2">No way to show progress</h4>
          <p class="text-base">
            Your coachees are growing, but you have no clear way to show them
            — or their sponsors — how far they have come.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-editorial p-8">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary-light flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-2">Admin overload</h4>
          <p class="text-base">
            Spending more time writing up notes, chasing actions, and managing
            logistics than actually coaching.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-editorial p-8">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary-light flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 0 1 3.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 0 0 3 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-2">Hard to evidence impact</h4>
          <p class="text-base">
            When accreditation bodies or clients ask for evidence of your
            coaching impact, you are left scrambling through old files.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── How Mentric Helps ─── -->
  <section class="bg-background">
    <div class="section-container py-14">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-14">
        <p class="category-label mb-4">How Mentric helps</p>
        <h2>Everything you need, nothing you don't</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Mentric is purpose-built for coaches. Every feature is designed to
          save you time and make your practice shine.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 1: One place -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center mb-16">
        <div>
          <p class="category-label mb-3">Your hub</p>
          <h3 class="mb-4">One place for your entire practice</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            All your coachees, sessions, goals, and assessments live in a single,
            beautifully organised dashboard. No more switching between apps or
            losing track of where things are.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-muted">Complete coachee profiles at a glance</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-muted">Session history, goals, and assessments in one view</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-muted">Works on desktop, tablet, and mobile</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
          <img src="/images/command-center.webp" alt="Mentric coach command center showing coachee list, session schedule, and practice overview in one dashboard" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2: Structured journeys -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center mb-16">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
          <img src="/images/goals-pipeline.webp" alt="Goals pipeline view showing coachee development stages from Awareness through to Mastery with milestone tracking" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <p class="category-label mb-3">Coaching framework</p>
          <h3 class="mb-4">Structured coaching journeys</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Guide each coachee through meaningful stages of development — from
            Awareness through to Mastery. Set goals with clear milestones and
            let AI suggest focus areas based on assessment results.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-muted">Stage-based progression (Awareness, Development, Mastery)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-muted">Goals with milestones and evidence tracking</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-muted">AI-powered goal suggestions from assessment data</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3: Assessments -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center mb-16">
        <div>
          <p class="category-label mb-3">Measure growth</p>
          <h3 class="mb-4">Professional assessments</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Build custom assessments tailored to your methodology, or start
            with ready-made templates. Run 360-degree feedback with full
            respondent management and track how scores improve over time.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-muted">Custom assessment builder with flexible question types</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-muted">360-degree feedback with respondent tracking</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-muted">Score trends and improvement analytics</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
          <img src="/images/assessments.webp" alt="Professional assessments page showing custom assessment builder with 360-degree feedback and score tracking" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 4: Session management -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center mb-16">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
          <img src="/images/sessions.webp" alt="Session management view with scheduled coaching sessions, AI-powered summaries, and follow-up actions" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <p class="category-label mb-3">Save hours every week</p>
          <h3 class="mb-4">Effortless session management</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Schedule sessions across any platform — Zoom, Teams, phone, or
            in-person. Let AI handle the heavy lifting with automatic
            summaries and transcription, so you can stay present during the
            conversation.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-muted">Multi-platform scheduling (Zoom, Teams, phone, in-person)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-muted">AI-powered session summaries and transcription</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-muted">Capture notes and assign follow-up actions</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 5: Resources -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center mb-16">
        <div>
          <p class="category-label mb-3">Knowledge sharing</p>
          <h3 class="mb-4">Share resources that matter</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Build your own resource library and share articles, videos, and
            documents directly with coachees. See what they have engaged with
            so you can tailor conversations accordingly.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-muted">Personal resource library with categories</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-muted">Share articles, videos, and documents with coachees</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-muted">Engagement tracking to inform your coaching</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
          <img src="/images/resources.webp" alt="Resource library with categorised articles, videos, and documents shared with coachees" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 6: CPD -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center mb-16">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
          <img src="/images/cpd.webp" alt="CPD tracking dashboard showing coaching hours, reflective practice journal, and accreditation evidence" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <p class="category-label mb-3">Professional development</p>
          <h3 class="mb-4">Track your CPD</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Your coaching hours are logged automatically as you work. Keep a
            reflective practice journal and have everything you need ready
            when accreditation bodies come knocking.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-muted">Automatic coaching hours logging</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-muted">Reflective practice journal</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-muted">Ready-made evidence for accreditation bodies</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 7: Insights -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="category-label mb-3">Stay informed</p>
          <h3 class="mb-4">Insights at a glance</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Your dashboard gives you a clear picture of your coaching activity,
            coachee progress, and engagement trends. Ask questions about your
            practice and let AI surface the answers.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-muted">Activity dashboard with key metrics</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-muted">Coachee progress and engagement analytics</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              <span class="text-muted">AI-powered queries about your practice</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
          <img src="/images/analytics.webp" alt="Analytics dashboard with coaching activity metrics, coachee progress trends, and engagement analytics" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-editorial-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Coachee Experience ─── -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="section-container py-14">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <p class="category-label mb-4">The coachee experience</p>
        <h2>Your coachees will love it too</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Mentric gives every coachee their own space to engage with the
          coaching process — a professional experience that reflects well
          on your practice.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="card-editorial p-6 text-center">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary-light flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 6A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 6 3.75h2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 10.5 6v2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25H6a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25V6ZM3.75 15.75A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 6 13.5h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25 2.25V18a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25H6A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 3.75 18v-2.25ZM13.5 6a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25-2.25H18A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 20.25 6v2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 18 10.5h-2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25V6ZM13.5 15.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25-2.25H18a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25 2.25V18A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 18 20.25h-2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25v-2.25Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-base font-semibold mb-1">Personal dashboard</h4>
          <p class="text-sm">Their own space to track goals, sessions, and progress</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-editorial p-6 text-center">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary-light flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 3 19.875v-6.75ZM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V8.625ZM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V4.125Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-base font-semibold mb-1">Goal tracking</h4>
          <p class="text-sm">Milestones, evidence, and clear progress indicators</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-editorial p-6 text-center">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary-light flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
